latestPosts.caption:
DIRTY CUT 2025 - PRATIBHA RANTA 9/17

In Laapataa Ladies, Pratibha Ranta (@pratibha_ranta) brought heart, humour, and something you couldn’t quite put your finger on—and it stuck. The role bagged her an entire award season’s roster in one clean swipe and kicked open doors to a new wave of stories. She’s on the grind but not chasing instant gratification. A fledgeling on the cusp of megawatt stardom, the dirty cut 2025 cover star is slowly and surely building her icon status.
 
In collaboration with @nothingindia

Happy world environment day 💚

Nature is what drives me the most.
A walk uphill reminded me of where I come from and where I aim to go.
My walks have always been moments of introspection.
 
After the release of Laapataa Ladies, my people showered me with so much love.
It was truly beautiful being back home.
Thankyou so much everyone ♥️
